    "custom_liquid_DCQyKF": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"uspaFitHero\">\n  <div class=\"uspaFitHero__inner\">\n\n    <h1>USPA Men's Polo Shirt Style Guide: Find the Perfect Fit</h1>\n\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">Find the Perfect Fit</p>\n\n    <p>\n      USPA Polo shirts are iconic pieces of men’s fashion, combining elegance and comfort. USPA, the iconic French brand, offers a variety of Polo shirt fits to suit all styles and body types. In this guide, we help you choose the USPA Polo shirt fit that suits you best.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>Why Choose a USPA Polo Shirt?</h2>\n\n    <p>\n      USPA, a symbol of French fashion, embodies elegance and innovation. In the late 1920s, René USPA, seeking greater freedom of movement on the tennis court, cut the sleeves off his shirt, thus creating the first Polo shirt. This revolutionary invention, born out of a need for comfort and performance, took the world by storm and became a symbol of timeless style.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n      Whether you're looking for a relaxed weekend look or a polished outfit for the office, USPA offers Polo shirts that combine style and functionality for every occasion. Each fit is designed to provide optimal freedom of movement, true to René USPA's innovative spirit.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>The Different USPA Polo Shirt Fits</h2>\n\n    <h3>1. Slim Fit</h3>\n    <p>\n      The slim fit is ideal for those who prefer a tailored look without feeling too tight. These Polo shirts hug the body's shape while offering freedom of movement. Perfect for a modern and sleek style, USPA slim fit Polo shirts pair well with tailored trousers and structured jackets. They are perfect for a sophisticated and contemporary look.\n    </p>\n\n    <h3>2. Regular Fit</h3>\n    <p>\n      The regular fit is a timeless classic that suits all body types. With a standard size and a slightly tailored cut, these Polo shirts offer optimal comfort and an elegant silhouette. They are versatile and can be worn with jeans, chinos, or shorts for a casual or dressed-up look. USPA regular fit Polo shirts are perfect for a classic and enduring style.\n    </p>\n\n    <h3>3. Classic Fit</h3>\n    <p>\n      The classic fit is the original USPA Polo shirt cut, designed to provide freedom of movement with elegance. Comfortable and iconic, this cut offers great freedom of movement thanks to its slightly looser fit. USPA classic fit Polo shirts are perfect for those seeking a timeless and elegant look while prioritizing comfort.\n    </p>\n\n    <h3>4. Loose Fit</h3>\n    <p>\n      For those who prioritize comfort, the loose fit is the ideal choice. These oversized Polo shirts offer a more relaxed fit, perfect for casual days or activities requiring greater freedom of movement. Pair them with relaxed trousers or shorts for a laid-back and comfortable look. USPA loose fit Polo shirts are perfect for a relaxed and easy-going style.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>In Conclusion</h2>\n    <p>\n      USPA men’s Polo shirts are an elegant and versatile choice for any occasion. By choosing the fit that best suits your body type or current mood, you can create stylish and comfortable outfits. Explore the USPA Polo shirt collection and find your perfect fit today!\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  /* BLUE PANEL + WHITE BORDER FRAME (like screenshot) */\n  .uspaFitHero{\n    background:#0e2340;\n    color:#ffffff;\n\n    border:2px solid #ffffff;     /* ✅ border around the whole panel */\n    margin:30px;                   /* ✅ creates the white “margin” around the panel */\n    padding:110px 20px 120px;\n\n    margin-bottom:0 !important;    /* your original */\n  }\n\n  .uspaFitHero__inner{\n    max-width:920px;\n    margin:0 auto;\n    text-align:center;\n  }\n\n  .uspaFitHero h1{\n    font-size:38px;\n    font-weight:400;\n    letter-spacing:.2px;\n    line-height:1.2;\n    margin-bottom:18px;\n    white-space:nowrap;\n  }\n\n  .uspaFitHero .subtitle{\n    font-size:20px;\n    font-weight:600;\n    margin-bottom:35px;\n    color:#ffffff;\n  }\n\n  .uspaFitHero h2{\n    font-size:24px;\n    font-weight:500;\n    margin:55px 0 18px;\n    color:#ffffff;\n  }\n\n  .uspaFitHero h3{\n    font-size:20px;\n    font-weight:500;\n    margin:40px 0 12px;\n    color:#ffffff;\n  }\n\n  .uspaFitHero p{\n    font-size:19px;\n    line-height:1.8;\n    margin-bottom:26px;\n    color:#ffffff;\n  }\n\n  /* Kill theme spacing around this section */\n  .shopify-section:has(.uspaFitHero){\n    margin-bottom:0 !important;\n    padding-bottom:0 !important;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width:990px){\n    .uspaFitHero h1{\n      white-space:normal;\n      font-size:30px;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width:749px){\n    .uspaFitHero{\n      padding:70px 18px 80px;\n      margin:18px;                 /* tighter inset on mobile */\n    }\n    .uspaFitHero p{ font-size:16px; }\n    .uspaFitHero h2{ font-size:20px; }\n    .uspaFitHero h3{ font-size:18px; }\n  }\n</style>",
